<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.2.10">
<l>eṉṟu meṉakkiṉi yāṉai yeṉmaṇi vaṇṇaṉai</l>
<l>kaṉṟiṉ piṉpōkki ṉēṉeṉṟa cōtai kaḻaṟiya</l>
<l>poṉtikaḻ māṭap putuvai yarkōṉpaṭ ṭaṉcol</l>
<l>iṉtamiḻ mālaikaḷ vallavark kiṭaril laiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who can master [this] garland of sweet Tamil,</l>
<l>the words of the scholar king of those of Putuvai,</l>
<l rend="indent"> with mansions that glitter with gold,</l>
<l>“I sent my jewel hued one, him who is always sweet to me, after the calves,”</l>
<l rend="indent">that were spoken by Yaśodā,</l>
<l>there is no suffering.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
